to add new user send POST request under /users/signup:
{
	"username": "username",
	"password": "password",
	"firstname": "firstname",
	"lastname": "lastname",
	"email": "email",
	"phone": "phone",
	"address": "address",
	"city": "city",
	"afm": "afm"
}

to see web token contents:
https://jwt.io/

Front-end prerequisites:
node.js (run node -v to check version)
npm install -g @angular/cli
npm install ngx-pagination --save
npm install jwt-decode --save

To run front-end:
cd frontend
ng serve -o (it should open the app in a new window in the browser)

to post an auction: 
{
	"name": "blue bike",
	"category": "vehicle",
	"location": "Athens",
	"country": "Greece",
	"currently": "120",
	"started": "3/4/19",
	"ends": "3/6/19",
	"description": "the bike is actually red",
	"seller": "5d4a788e729c8410124f98de"
}

to update:
[
	{"property": "name",
	"value": "red bike"},
	{"property": "currently",
	"value": "213"}
]

